Package communication.messages.vmo

In this package are located all classes which represents request sent from server to process task in virtual machine executions

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    VirtualMachineAddTimeMessage
    Represents message to add time to execution
    VirtualMachineRestartMessage
    Represents message to restart physical machine
    VirtualMachineSaveImageMessage
    Represents message to send current execution to server
    VirtualMachineSaveImageResponse
    Represents response to send current execution to server
    VirtualMachineStartMessage
    Represents message to start a virtual machine execution
    VirtualMachineStartResponse
    Represents response from agent to start a virtual machine execution
    VirtualMachineStopMessage
    Represents message to stop a virtual machine execution
    VirtualNetInterfaceComponent
    Component in virtual interface start message Specifies net interface in a virtual machine
